Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.98,0:01:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.52,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.37,0:02:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3\N以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.84,0:02:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.14,0:02:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.94,0:02:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『進入大氣層』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些肥皂和毛巾是給你的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你舒服地踏上地球土地上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要！我要你修好它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.69,0:03:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵！快完成了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯，可以給我看看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥！你會修理嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能修好它嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你，自從他父親去世後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就一直拿著這輛車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是戰死的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是在上次的一年戰爭中死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽應仍在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸是在SIDE 7號內失蹤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，修好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便和孫兒一起回故鄉住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來以為到死也回不了地球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未去SIDE 7號前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在南美洲經營咖啡園的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！這便是咖啡豆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.25,0:04:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回地球後我絕不會再離開的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是ZION軍的侵略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或是聯邦軍的逼遷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要將這副老骨頭埋在地球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有25分鐘就進入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！有信心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試過用太空滑翔機進入地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但當時的聯絡網已安排好一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且體積也比不上母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本航行方法是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照密斯號的指示便可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞會讓我們回去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一心進入大氣層就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我會的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小伙子，你聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.36,0:04:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！聽到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好進入大氣層嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會先用密斯號上的小飛船引導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以速度會比你們快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬別要落後！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改用自動控制降落大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.01,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備衝入大氣層！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞的軍艦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時未改變位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是有另一艘船正在接近中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道又要進行補給？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，在這時侯補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這豈不是等於放棄追蹤嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有3台ZAKU送來，真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20分鐘後就會到達大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到目前為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍未有人試過這時候去攻擊敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被地球的引力吸入去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.79,0:05:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論什麼也好都會成為灰燼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，敵人為了進入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須要投入全部注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對起來也是個突襲的良機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個目標是『木馬』戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二個目標是敵人機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時間只有2分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望各位會完成這次的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解散！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.01,0:06:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會先進去小飛船內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而密斯號拋出小飛船後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會獨自回月神二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有信心小飛船會安全嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來就沒信心擺脫敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可能會有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如他們真的正在補給的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許仍有機會安全到達地球的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信不會追來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從來都這樣樂觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，也相信因此才活到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們出發吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.25,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.89,0:06:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小飛船準備分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.18,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望ZION軍不會來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小飛船脫離密斯號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base正在後面跟隨著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請母艦各隊員注意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本艦會在8分鐘後衝入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人請扣好安全帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有震動別站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各戰鬥、控制員請回自己崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.65,0:07:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM作好隨時出發準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必要時緊急出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的畫面已調至最大極限！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接觸時間在30秒後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開特別門，發射GUNDAM出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，四分鐘後你要回來母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.61,0:07:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不願意被燒成炭呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面坐標R3度發現有4台ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.68,0:07:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞應該沒有機動戰士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對嗎？雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人掩護White Base嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面的機關炮由良和凱掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.66,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要注意飛行高度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時又怎可注意飛行高度呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話會害死人的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來那機動戰士又出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杜力，你掩護我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們分左右夾擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射分體飛船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭   發射火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面有火箭來了，李中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你降低高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以回轉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在回轉會被擊中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太遠了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第2排飛彈、避開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面掩護的彈幕太薄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特隊長，請冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家還不太懂得使用呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.67,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙壞了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來就不會用飛彈的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你還未想死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快點使它活動吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊有說明書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.42,0:09:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才修理遙控車的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會將敵人打敗的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要追到夏亞的動作才行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他對戰過多少次呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想接近母艦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.99,0:10:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，別太注意夏亞一個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們正在攻擊小飛船！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.07,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.89,0:10:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次想不背著夏亞不成了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太大意了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們休想得手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟！火箭炮沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，可以發射激光機槍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.82,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不可以射出激光機槍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我查看有否其它武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你負責左面的炮台！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我負責炮台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從未試用過呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，隼人，他們太接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用火箭，使用機關鎗吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！現只有GUNDAM鐵球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總比沒有好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以發射的話通知你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請繼續留意通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校...救命啊！      少校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校...少校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼總是打不中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準星壞了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.05,0:11:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我現在發射GUNDAM鐵球了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對速度實在太快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒彈藥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏差似乎太大了！   沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這難以擔保...可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉，你的宇宙飛行服！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！空氣正在洩出！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快，先修理小飛船！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面著火了！快滅火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.20,0:12:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，你的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先修理飛船，一會才理傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！可以輕點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,密斯號小飛船中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可以衝入大氣層嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小飛船會無法支持的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.18,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小飛船可以收納入母艦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得到吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳叫阿姆羅去引開兩台ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.65,0:13:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成！戰況太激烈，沒有餘力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加速百分之十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已到小飛船前面了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我們要收納小飛船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，良，協助掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙別亂動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開特別門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小飛船聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射激光吸引光，預備照準！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.11,0:13:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候竟用吸引光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,激光吸引光發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你們幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑這點怎可打倒敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,採用接近戰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣發揮不到ZAKU的長處！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...這很危險的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看準弱點進攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆！跟我來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，少校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會跟著來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.54,0:14:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然右手動不了，但仍可用左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就太好了，你要繼續支持下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起去幹掉那機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，有機動戰士由艦底攻過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.82,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太樂觀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右舷中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊加劇了！各崗位加強戎備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,損壞的地方用「修補汽球」！的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第4區快做修補工作！沒人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐，我也要去作戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為作戰是去玩耍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打仗又如何？很令人害怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要射擊的地方在那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是35號室吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但瞄準那方向呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰運氣吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的目的是要牽制GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.27,0:15:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM的駕駛員愈來愈進步了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯，來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！快回來母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快沒時間了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞，看我的最後一擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古朗，回杜力的飛艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古朗   古朗   聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入大氣層，關上大閘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用特別門收GUNDAM回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮台全部退回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！用母艦後面閘門回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，但機槍仍剩下子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先收拾那ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不宜再戰了！回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！打開閘門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.84,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古朗，回來，纏鬥下去沒好結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去，大氣層的磨擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會使GUNDAM粉碎的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！快回來！別理ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.35,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，我的任務是要將White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和GUNDAM運回地球聯邦總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫GUNDAM回來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己去說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你任由他胡來才會有這局面的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不派GUNDAM出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家早已沒命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉，請你坐好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有危險的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面已升起冷卻設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你準備上軍事法庭吧！知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！為什麼還不回來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.16,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想不到下降的速度會這麼快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古朗呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已無能為力了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.67,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校   救命...少校...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我，我無法減速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布朗，我們的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒有降落大氣層的性能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.45,0:17:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你的死是不會白費的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你纏著那聯邦的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能把它擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明瞭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知如何安全進入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕得及嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是冷卻裝備，先接通線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防熱罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝甲板的溫度下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，怎樣才可著陸呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為電波的干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法確定GUNDAM現在的位置！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！阿姆囉！請回答！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來短時間是難以聯絡得上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,位置一直沒變！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有發生燃燒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會這樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.81,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道機動戰士可單獨進入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看是沒可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但木馬戰艦又可自由進入地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能真的可以...真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.73,0:19:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高度32、31、30...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.27,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,29、27、25、24...20
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.37,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,19、16、14、12、11
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣可支持住嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等無線電回復後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即為我叫卡爾瑪上校出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在才知少校的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.96,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的原意是即使入大氣層時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能消滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要將改變他們進入地球的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使敵軍進入我們的勢力範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是雙管齊下的戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭是要靠智慧的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然要動腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校的通信來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎？『紅色彗星』？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣叫我，我也要好好稱呼你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！看你的面色很差呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有聽過敵人的V作戰計劃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經查出那真相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經損失8台機動戰士了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是損失慘重了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.50,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍員的如此利害嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已將他們引到你那處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,功勞就由你去奪取了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲些我會到你那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我先多謝你的知會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會派戰鬥空母出動的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.62,0:20:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高度5萬3千，減速情況良好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在回復水平角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽到嗎？阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！現在已可回復通信了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.36,0:20:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你回復吧！阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畫面恢復原狀了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是GUNDAM！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.01,0:21:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會我要好好教訓他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有這麼利害的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定可以戰勝ZION軍的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通信回復正常，我現在回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訊號良好，阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.73,0:21:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可停在甲板任何位置上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！是地球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部是陸地呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是叫做海的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.25,0:21:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路還是初次看地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏是由海和陸地所構成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大自然星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是預定的降落點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是現時的航道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼一回事？布萊特君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.37,0:22:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，這是ZION的勢力範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不如先去讓醫生看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.92,0:22:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞的戰略相當成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.92,0:22:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們又中了他的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.92,0:22:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.72,0:22:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也要突破出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.05,0:22:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.67,0:22:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來夏亞說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這戰艦和一般的規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.95,0:23:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相差得太大了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞少校的宇宙飛船來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.76,0:23:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收容吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.78,0:23:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡爾瑪·薩比的機動力將White Base逼到絕境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.45,0:23:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與正規軍的戰鬥是不容許一瞬的鬆懈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而阿姆羅他們更因為地球的重力而陷入苦戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『卡爾瑪出擊』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.31,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

